===Haproxy===
*简介

HAProxy is a TCP/HTTP reverse proxy which is particularly suited for high availability environments(非常适合高可用环境). <br/>
Indeed, it can(可以完成如下工作):<br/>
- route HTTP requests depending on statically assigned cookies ; (使用http cookies 路由http 请求)<br/>
- spread the load among several servers while assuring server persistence through the use of HTTP cookies ; (均衡负载的同时使用http cookies 确保服务器持久化) <br/>
- switch to backup servers in the event a main one fails ;( 服务器故障时自动切换到备用节点) <br/>
- accept connections to special ports dedicated to service monitoring ; (接受(并转发)连接到 专用的 服务监控 端口)<br/>
- stop accepting connections without breaking existing ones ;(拒绝(超出上限的)新连接而不影响现有连接) <br/>
- add/modify/delete HTTP headers both ways ; (增删改 http header) <br/>
- block requests matching a particular pattern ;( 阻塞 匹配特定模式的请求) <br/>
- hold clients to the right application server depending on application cookies.( 使用application coolkie 保证客户端与application server 的对应.) <br/>
- report detailed status as HTML pages to authenticated users from an URI intercepted from the application.( 以html网页形式向授权用户汇报 application的详细状态 )<br/>
<br/>
It needs very little resource. Its event-driven architecture allows it to easily handle thousands of simultaneous  connections  on hundreds of instances without risking the system's stability.<br/>
Haproxy 消耗非常少的资源.它的事件驱动架构允许它轻松处理数以百计虚拟机上的数以千计的并发连接而不损失系统稳定性.<br/>


*配置文件 示范
<console>
[root@network 8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485]# cat conf 
global
   daemon                  # 后台运行haproxy进程
   user nobody             # user
   group haproxy           # group
   log /dev/log local0     # 
   log /dev/log local1 notice
   stats socket /var/lib/neutron/lbaas/8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485/sock \
   mode 0666 level user

defaults
   log global         # 日志文件输出定向
   retries 3          # 3次连接失败就认为服务器不可用，主要通过后面的check检查
   option redispatch      # 
   timeout connect 5000
   timeout client 50000
   timeout server 50000
frontend c4c49fc1-bf10-4270-bc20-02b93439897f
   option tcplog
   bind 172.172.172.7:80
   mode http
   default_backend 8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485
   maxconn 100
   option forwardfor
backend 8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485
   mode http
   balance leastconn
   option forwardfor
   server 0c7d3741-df7b-4bf3-9396-14cc3c05b5a5 172.172.172.4:80 weight 100
   server 44c18162-301e-42f3-9f0a-5522f426412f 172.172.172.6:80 weight 100
   server c96132b8-101e-4e5e-9927-07708b34ae77 172.172.172.5:80 weight 100
</console>

*启动haproxy进程 示范
<console>
[root@network 8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485]# ps aux | grep haproxy
root      1324  0.0  0.0 112640   964 pts/0    S+   17:24   0:00 grep --color=auto haproxy
nobody    5818  0.0  0.0  49832  1660 ?        Ss   12:48   0:00 haproxy -f \
/var/lib/neutron/lbaas/8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485/conf -p \
/var/lib/neutron/lbaas/8f09dbaf-0c78-48f1-8b80-662e75036485/pid -sf 27485 
</console>

*结合neutron lbaas来学习

上述配置文件是探索 负载均衡 时创建的样例负载均衡的配置，参考链接:http://192.168.100.158/mw/index.php/Lbaas.
对比负载均衡资源池,VIP,后端RIP(即members)的配置与Happroxy进程配置文件中的选项.首先查看VIP.
<console>   
[root@controller ~(keystone_admin)]# neutron lb-vip-list
+-----+------+---------------+----------+----------------+--------+
| id  | name | address       | protocol | admin_state_up | status |
+-----+------+---------------+----------+----------------+--------+
| c4..| VIP  | 172.172.172.7 | HTTP     | True           | ACTIVE |
+-----+------+---------------+----------+----------------+--------+
</console>

